categories: Category:Cut content from Star Wars Galaxies

nodes.text: Reely Sugg was a male Chiss who lived during the time of the Galactic Civil War.

Reely Sugg appears in the directory tree files for the 2003 massively multiplayer online role-playing game Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided. According to these files, Sugg would have been in some way involved with the 2005 expansion pack, Rage of the Wookiees. However, Sugg is not known to have appeared on the video game's live servers as a proper non-player character. Nevertheless, an emulated depiction pulled from this character's Interchange File Format reveals what he would have looked like if he were added to the game.
